description:
Dane is only 24, but he has a very mature way about him. I guessed right away that he's Italian and from New York. He's straight and says he's juggling 2 or 3 girls right now.
He's kind of demure and definitely the strong, silent type. Once I got him going, though, he was all smiles and couldn't wait to bust his nut on camera!
title: Dane
